@startuml
title Decision flow: New Application vs Reissue vs New Job

start

:What changed?;

if (Is the worker doing a different job?) then (Yes)
  :Create/Invite a NEW APPLICATION;
  :Person completes application workflow;
  :Application accepted;
  stop
else (No)

  if (Is this a new season\non an existing job?) then (Yes)
    :Create a NEW JOB with the new dates;
    :Invite worker to the new job;
    :Person completes application workflow;
    :Application accepted;
    stop
  else (No)

    if (Only pay or conditions changed?) then (Yes)
      :Update job conditions OR personal conditions;
      :Reissue agreement;
      :Person completes agreement workflow;
      :Agreement accepted;
      stop
    else (Not sure)
      :Contact PICMI support with:

      * worker name
      * current job
      * intended change
      * whether dates or role changed;
      stop
    endif

  endif

endif

@enduml
